@startmindmap
skinparam BackgroundColor #f7f7f7
skinparam DefaultFontName Helvetica
<style>
Node {
  Padding 8
  Margin 12
  BackgroundColor #fff2cc
  LineColor #7f6000
  LineThickness 2
  RoundCorner 12
  FontSize 14
}
rootNode {
  BackgroundColor #d5e8d4
  FontColor #274e13
}
.Important {
  BackgroundColor #dae8fc
  FontColor #1155cc
  HorizontalAlignment Right
}
arrow {
  LineColor #999999
  LineThickness 2
}
</style>
* Styled release plan
** Goals <<Important>>
*** Compatibility
*** Documentation
** Delivery
*** Automation
@endmindmap
